@startuml
title Layered Architecture của Backend API (tổng quan)

top to bottom direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

actor "Client\n(Frontend SPA / n8n)" as Client

package "Presentation Layer\n(API)" as Presentation {
  [Controllers\n(REST Endpoints)] as Controllers
}

package "Application Layer\n(Use cases)" as Application {
  [Services\n(Business logic)] as Services
}

package "Infrastructure Layer\n(Data access + External)" as Infrastructure {
  [Repository / Prisma] as Repo
  [External Services\n(ví dụ: Cloudinary)] as External
}

database "Data Layer\n(PostgreSQL)" as DB

Client --> Controllers : HTTP/JSON
Controllers --> Services
Services --> Repo
Repo --> DB
Services --> External

note right of Controllers
Cross-cutting concerns (không đi sâu chi tiết):
- Auth Guard / Role Guard
- ValidationPipe (DTO)
- Interceptor (chuẩn hoá response)
- Logging
end note

@enduml
